{
  "stem": "24171.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It's-- it was-- they said that it's coming to an end.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You know, there was always rumors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Oh--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had another name there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A fortune teller, because in the-- there, in the other end of the barrack, there were the same people, which-- we were together in Guben.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a mother with a daughter, too-- Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and-- and they kept on-- are we gonna-- what's gonna happen?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I kept-- I kept on telling lies for them, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, I heard that the sky is nearing the end.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it's going to be better.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And how many times did someone here say-- then it was allowed to walk around between the thing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they said, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's kind of a fortune woman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Come on, tell us something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Do you heard something-- every-- the thing-- things like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, we tried to cheer ourselves up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then, I-- when I felt a little bit better from-- from the typhoid fever, I-- while I-- again, start volunteering.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because they said, you know, as people start dying terrible from the typhoid, oh!",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I remember a thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a very-- she was a very kind of-- with me-- kind as a-- a woman.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as we were sleeping-- oh, we were fighting for sleeping, because we didn't have a place inside to sleep.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in the corridor, we-- we reserved places, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Fast-- as soon as we was allowed to get out, we spread that blanket, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were guarding it all the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now somebody else shouldn't come and take it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she was always kind of like, clinging to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as we were sleeping there-- and she was kind of by the wall.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was laying this way.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
